Print the CLI version

Usage:
  example version [flags]

Aliases:
  version, v

Examples:

./../../examples/cobra-alias/example version
./../../examples/cobra-alias/example version -o=json
./../../examples/cobra-alias/example version -o=yaml
./../../examples/cobra-alias/example version -o=short


Flags:
  -h, --help            help for version
  -o, --output string   Output format. One of: json | pretty | short | yaml (default "pretty")
